OL,7,F"Since the start of our investigation,
OL,8,Fwe have expanded our work to
OL,9,Finvestigate a number of detailed
OL,10,Fcomplaints from the families affected.
OL,11,FAs a result, seven officers have been
OL,12,Fadvised that they are under
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,F"We continue to analyse a significant
OL,16,Fvolume of evidence and assess whether
OL,17,Fpolice actions following the missing
OL,18,Fperson reports were in accordance with
OL,19,Flocal and national policies and
OL,20,Fprocedures.
