OL,7,F"At the end of our investigation, we
OL,8,Fwill make decisions as to whether any
OL,9,Fofficer should face disciplinary
OL,10,Fproceedings and whether any matters
OL,11,Fshould be referred to the Crown
OL,12,FProsecution Service."
OL,14,F"While we have carried out additional
OL,15,Fwork to address the concerns raised,
OL,16,Fwe will conclude our investigation as
OL,17,Fsoon as possible. It is important for
OL,18,Fall concerned that our independent
OL,19,Finvestigation is comprehensive and
OL,20,Fthorough."
